name: BetaPro NASDAQ-100 -2x Daily Bear ETF
longDescription: QQD seeks daily investment results, before fees, expenses, distributions, brokerage commissions and other transaction costs, that endeavour to correspond to two times (200 percent) the inverse (opposite) of the daily performance of the NASDAQ-100 Index R. QQD does not seek to achieve its stated investment objective over a period of time greater than one day.
